summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Neax Tattoos MVP - Premium Landing Page with booking system. Backend APIs 100% functional, frontend 95% functional with complete booking flow working end-to-end.

minor_issues.issue: Duplicate seed data - creates 6 artists instead of 3, 8 services instead of 4
minor_issues.impact: UI shows duplicate content but functionality works

expected_limitations.impact: Booking confirmation emails will fail but booking creation works

ui_bugs.issue: Book Now button not visible in mobile header navigation
ui_bugs.workaround: Book Now button available in mobile menu and contact section

passed_tests: Landing page loads with hero, artists, services, gallery, testimonials, contact sections
Desktop and mobile navigation menu functionality
User registration flow (email, password, name, phone)
User login flow with JWT authentication
4-step booking wizard: Service → Artist → Date/Time → Confirm
Calendar date selection with future date navigation
Time slot selection (9 time slots available)
Complete booking submission and dashboard redirect
Anti-AI design theme implementation (Noir & Bone, sharp edges, glassmorphism)
action_item_for_main_agent: Minor fixes needed: 1) Fix duplicate seed data in /api/seed endpoint, 2) Add RESEND_API_KEY to enable email confirmations, 3) Ensure Book Now button visible in mobile header navigation. All core functionality working correctly.
